Hi Eric,

If you still have the receipt, tae the 009 electronic ignition back  
and exchange it for the version that fits your vacuum advance  
distributor. Otherwise sell it off on ebay or whatever.

If the bus is running well on the vacuum advance distributor then the  
009 will NOT be an upgrade.


Happy Trails,

